  "body": "<p>Need some fresh planning inspiration? Check out these amazing planner spreads from some incredibly talented ladies using my <a href=\"http://www.archerandolive.com/?aff=142\">2021 planner collab with Archer and Olive</a>!  </p><p>Scroll down for a closer look at each planner spread and make sure to follow these planner babes on Instagram too!</p>\n\n\n\n\n \n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616159431487-G77MZ08V2FL4QIHPDSUG/Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Inspiration.png\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n  \n<p>L to R, T to B - <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/planawayrenee/ \">@planawayrenee</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/theplannerteawithdani/ \">@theplannerteawithdani</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vanessapglass/\">@vanesspglass</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ajmcgarvey/ \">@ajmcgarvey</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/myhappyplaceplans/ \">@myhappplaceplans</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thelifefacilitator/ \">@thelifefacilitator</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/arterestically/ \">@arterestically</a>, <a href=\" https://www.instagram.com/lovelearncreate2400/ \">@lovelearncreate2400</a>, <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/momruncraft/\">@momruncraft</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n \n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLUjn4pJWxV/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616161546227-S3YVP96BGN3GI5CJVCT0/How+to+Use+Photos+in+Your+Weekly+Memory+Planner\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616161981841-W5M3AJKO40528QWNEFZP/The+Planner+Tea+with+Dani+-+Washi+Tape.png\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>This spread by <a href=\"theplannerteawithdani\">@theplannerteawithdani</a> uses two of my favorite scrapbooking supplies - washi tape and watercolors! </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>I love how <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/planawayrenee/ \">@planawayrenee</a> incorporates photos in her memory planner! Click the images to see the spread on Instagram.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLkIsm-ppHA/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616162406199-I5QT7TZC94WRJQ28XMA7/Journaling+and+statement+cutouts+.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLr04zbJILq/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616162790029-GNTQC1WRBDUV0XHXF91Y/Neutral+watercolors.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>This spread by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ajmcgarvey/ \">@ajmcgarvey</a> is so calming. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Lots of journaling from <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/vanessapglass/\">@vanessapglass</a> and large cutouts make a big impact! </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CKPQI5eJQtR/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616162994922-K1949ZUW846FRWSITY6D/Bright+and+colorful+.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLw1YicJLcs/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616163073482-ZZZXB87U952STHLM6FH5/Muted+colors+.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>But sometimes it’s nice to have more muted, pastel tones too! <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thelifefacilitator/ \">@thelifefacilitator</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Bright, colorful spreads always make me happy! <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/myhappyplaceplans/ \">@myhappyplaceplans</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMDMZb9ltus/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616163273993-NR6CIFLZG2BNGHHTWLGU/hand+drawn+illustrations+.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CKgWw90JDdK/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616163408457-IH6IM9ZACBYV8ZSUQ11R/color+coordinated.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Here’s another fun, colorful spread by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lovelearncreate2400/ \">@lovelearncreate2400</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Look at these beautiful hand-drawn illustrations  and lettering by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/arterestically/ \">@arterestically</a>!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<a href=\"Creative balance of journaling and other elements! @momruncraft\">\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1616163513422-AC1O4ZTKU8W75680DW2L/Balance+of+journaling+and+pops+of+color.png\"/>\n\n\n</a>\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Love this creative balance of journaling and other elements! <a href=\" https://www.instagram.com/momruncraft/ \">@momruncraft</a></p><p>I love seeing your planner pages! Make sure to tag me on Instagram @amytangerine and use #amytangerine and #AmyforAO when you share your planner spreads! </p><p>You can still get the <a href=\"http://www.archerandolive.com/?aff=142\">2021 Red Undated Planner</a> from Archer and Olive. Use code <strong>AMYTANGERINE</strong> for 10% off any order! </p>"
}